title: Star Trek Continues E04 The White Iris.mp4
description:
Star Trek Continues Episode 4 - The White Iris

Kirk is violently attacked while welcoming a new planet to the Federation.  The injury unlocks feelings of guilt which Kirk must address or else be unable to save the new Federation member planet from a catastrophic attack originating on a rival planet.  The only thing which can help Kirk is forgiveness from his unborn daughter
